en_202127_0	Showing compassion and kindness in response to a plea, made by a helpless civilian in Sivamnagar, Puwarasankulam area, the 61 Division Headquarters of the Security Force Headquarters-Wanni provided a stock of raw materials for completion of his house on Thursday (10).
en_202127_1	Brigadier K. D. C. G J Thilakarathne, General Officer Commanding, 61 Division took steps to provide the hapless civilians with tin sheets, cement bags and bricks for completion of his house.
en_202127_2	Troops also facilitated transport of those items to the location.
en_202127_3	The beneficiary was also gifted with several saplings of economic value for planting in his garden where the house was being completed.
